CVE-2026-29786
CVE-2026-31802

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# esbuild binary (Go 1.20.12) bundled by @modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem
#
# esbuild is a JS bundler compiled with Go 1.20.12 and shipped as a prebuilt
# binary inside the MCP server npm package. These stdlib CVEs affect the Go
# runtime used to compile esbuild — we cannot upgrade the binary without a new
# upstream release of esbuild or the MCP server package.
# The esbuild binary is only used for bundling JS at build time; it is NOT
# executed at runtime by our application.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

